Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.19,0:00:04.23,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:21.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You've finally made your way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:24.79,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Mifune.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:28.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Star, on stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:31.26,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,One win and one loss...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:33.51,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This will decide who's the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:38.72,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:41.77,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you who's the winner once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:53.32,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki, you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:54.28,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:00:58.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the path of a demon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:00.41,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,or the path of the warrior?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:03.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Star...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.54,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,On which path will you walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:02:46.35,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:50.44,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Is giving Shibusen this Demon Tool really the right thing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:55.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If honorable father is planning to use it to perform evil deeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:57.65,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,then when that time comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.91,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:02.45,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:04.33,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That. I wonder what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:10.87,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:29.73,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:38.69,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravery or Bloodshed: Decisive Battle, Mifune vs. Black Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:40.32,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:43.11,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Azusa, what's the situation out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.49,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say that it looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:48.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Although our forces in the front line are advancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.62,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,they're still a long way from infiltrating the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:51.54,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:55.33,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the situation at the relay stations?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:56.29,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.59,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the six relay stations,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:04.76,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,we've succeeded in suppressing enemy forces and destroying the relay stations in Oceania, Europe and the Middle East.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:08.93,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But the battle is on-going at the remaining three relay stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:09.81,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:14.98,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroying those relay stations would only delay the spread of insanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.32,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:21.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we defeat the Kishin, the situation will not become better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:22.65,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:25.32,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.16,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:28.28,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:31.25,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Death the Kid has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.16,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the Demon Tool?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:35.92,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem that he has succeeded in retrieving the tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:40.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.63,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:48.10,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,tell him to go to BJ and wait for us there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:51.47,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Kid, isn't this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:52.68,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:55.14,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,this is the room of that fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:00.65,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This Demon Tool, and Shibusen's inconsistent movements as of late...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:03.49,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth could they be hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:09.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything... lies beyond this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:28.76,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had seen at least some potential in you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:31.06,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems I've overestimated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:33.47,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What an arrogant fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:35.89,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking like you're better than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:38.48,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki, Ninja Blade mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:39.27,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,On it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:43.48,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Speed Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:50.07,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:53.29,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:59.79,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,So the rate of your Soul Resonance has increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:03.13,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,My blade and your speed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:05.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll see which is faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.80,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Infinite One Sword Style.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:09.80,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:19.10,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:23.48,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The real one...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:25.53,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,is up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:36.66,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:42.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Steel Fangs: Vertical Alignment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,First strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:44.75,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Second strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:46.63,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Third strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:49.59,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:57.39,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This kind of wound, I wouldn't even call it a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.35,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You have good eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.56,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You managed to dodge them the second before they stabbed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:05.57,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,As I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.99,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't beat him without using the Fey Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:12.32,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done a really good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.99,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What you did really helped us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:20.71,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Tool, if you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:23.13,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:28.59,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.72,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:34.60,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,About what this Demon Tool is,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:39.73,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,and what you are trying to achieve by using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:42.27,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:43.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:47.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about all those suspicious movements?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:50.15,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,And even when I asked, you'd find a way to avoid answering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:52.36,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're saying that it's okay to let me now just like tha-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:54.28,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:58.24,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't afford to let just anyone know what we were planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:00.08,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a top secret operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:05.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, we can't let those who take side with the Kishin know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:09.30,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're telling me that we were suspecting too much from the very beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.92,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:16.64,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that we have this Demon Tool in our hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:19.27,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,we can say that the hardship we endured wasn't for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:24.44,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, what exactly is this Demon Tool?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.73,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well you see, this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:31.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Eibon's last creation:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:35.24,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Eibon, the Demon Tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:09:12.15,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:14.53,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's follow the plan and barge in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:17.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay to march in there just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:19.03,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's our mission to infiltrate this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.54,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:24.33,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.46,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we go in like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.46,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:34.97,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Their castle is right in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.39,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.23,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Shibusen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:46.23,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,They're doing better than I've thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:48.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Mosquito...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.44,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What is taking you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:55.99,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me, but the enemies are putting up a tough fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:59.24,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, then use "that".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.91,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say "that"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But our forces are still out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Just use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.79,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:16.63,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would've thought that it would come to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:38.57,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,A new weapon that fires a compressed version of the wavelength released by the Kishin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:41.82,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one hit from this weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:43.41,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,and not only the enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:47.79,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,but everything that's caught up in the field will be completely decimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:53.96,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Witness the power of this new weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:10:59.30,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:09.69,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you looking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:12.06,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki, Fey Blade mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:12.77,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:25.45,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hold out very long with that body of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:26.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:29.25,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat you before that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Resonance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:44.97,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:54.81,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Such tremendous maliciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.61,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to choose the path of a demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:58.57,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:00.61,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:04.82,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking if you'll follow the path of a demon on your own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:06.41,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:08.74,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not taking orders from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:22.38,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Those eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:25.39,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,they look familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.98,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:36.36,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:38.82,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,No one ever told me that the castle can move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:51.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Archmage Eibon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:53.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:57.25,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, honorable father and Eibon are really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:12:59.34,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.76,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'll have to get straight to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:05.64,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to lend me the power of BREW.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:07.35,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You need BREW?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:12.64,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that coward and that spider witch, the world is in total chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.10,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Asura and Arachne?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:18.56,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,honorable father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:19.61,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.98,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the relationship between you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.11,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:29.24,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be necessary to let you know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:34.00,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, Eibon and I used to fight together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:38.42,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,A member of Shinigami-sama's Squadron of Eight,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:41.00,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Kishin, Asura's partner-in-arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:44.72,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That was who he was at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:49.60,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did he start research on the Demon Tools?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:51.89,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:54.27,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well you see, a lot happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:56.31,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that wasn't much of an explanation, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:58.48,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:01.57,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,He loved to play around with machineries, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:03.23,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't even bother to elaborate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:04.78,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:11.87,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It was originally intended to protect the order of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:15.12,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, the research on the Demon Tools started.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:18.25,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,As many ages as there can be,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:23.34,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,when there is a tool of great power, there'll always be those would challenge their own fate by taking that tool into their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:27.68,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,And the more powerful the tool,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:31.55,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,the greater the risk when those tools are used for evil deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:35.39,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, he continued to believe in human beings,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:38.77,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,and continued his research on more inventions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:40.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:47.57,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,it was at one point that Eibon's research began to focus in on only one particular field.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:49.61,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that field?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:53.08,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the research on immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:54.41,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:56.45,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:01.25,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What kind of twisted face is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:08.63,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Excalibur doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:09.13,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:11.72,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:13.51,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it really not matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:14.85,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.35,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are starting to look interesting anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:21.77,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Eibon's research on immortality was caused by the intertwining of fates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:28.15,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,And behind all of it, lies an untold sad story...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:30.57,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,the sickness of his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:35.91,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Eibon's research on immortality was all for the sake of saving the life of his most beloved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:38.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The research to surpass death itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:42.29,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how great the inventor is, it is still an impossible feat to achieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:46.30,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Even for the great philosopher, Eibon, it wasn't an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually the research reach a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:55.76,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,And the one who encouraged Eibon with the sweet words was none other than Arachne.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:59.85,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:01.35,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:03.10,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:07.69,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it when I'm listening to him, it sounds like nothing but lies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.74,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:10.49,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:11.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:12.11,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:14.91,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Together with Eibon's research on the Demon Tools,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.58,0:16:20.29,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,and also Arachne's forbidden research on the creation of the Demon Weapons,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:24.13,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,the Demon Tool BREW came into being.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:31.67,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, I had an encounter with a man that had same eyes as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:34.51,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,He, too, bore the tattoo of a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:47.82,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,He robbed the life of even those with a good heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:52.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You, the Star Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:57.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to stray from the path of the warrior to follow the path of the demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:16:59.79,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Path?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:02.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What a load of crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:05.50,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come here only to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:06.96,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:08.75,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.13,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop while you still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:12.38,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done listening to your nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:16.84,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're talking about the notorious Star Clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:20.68,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, listening to the story of a clan which got completely wiped out doesn't interest me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:23.89,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it doesn't interest you, the child of a demon shall always remain a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.85,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for you to cut your ties with that cursed clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:27.90,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:39.41,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with all this strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:40.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:42.54,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing as hardships in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:45.12,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Only winning or losing exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:50.42,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to cut even your own soul with the sword which you used to take so many lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:18:00.43,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the first to let me know what fear really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:04.77,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But even the man, who was feared as the demon itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:06.89,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,feared that he would one day be defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:10.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,and was trembling helplessly deep down in his soul, without being known by anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:12.57,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:14.90,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,For a samurai, you speak too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:18.74,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's defeat, I believe you've already got a taste of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:19.87,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:28.00,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,There was only one reason that had caused that man to lose his path.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:34.59,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,White Star, let's end this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:39.97,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You-!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:43.68,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no longer a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:52.57,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,He lost the battle against the darkness within himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:54.48,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:58.07,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you persist on fighting and choose the path of the demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:18:59.74,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:03.03,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,His soul was weak, that's why he lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:04.49,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:09.12,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,He was strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:26.93,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where stood, he'd reach up higher,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:28.73,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,and always pushed himself to the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:30.35,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:36.57,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,he broke away from the path of the warrior, and fell into the path of the demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.16,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:47.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Which path would you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:49.33,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the path of the demon,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:51.12,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,or the path or the warrior?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:55.75,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up already, you damn samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:20:00.13,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop ordering me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:16.57,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, he still chose to walk into the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:25.32,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,BLACK STAR!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:33.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The power's overwhelming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:36.59,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll enjoy killing each and everyone of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:48.51,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Excalibur, doesn't this feel like class reunion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:51.93,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you came all the way here to meet Eibon too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:52.77,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's only part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:57.52,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still another reason for me to have come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:21:00.44,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to help us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:01.49,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:03.03,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You're got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:06.32,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to only to observe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:10.16,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:15.25,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,BREW,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:17.17,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,unlock.
